Global, regional, and national burden of meningitis, 1990-2016: a systematic 
analysis for the Global Burden of Disease Study 2016.

GBD 2016 Meningitis Collaborators.

Collaborators: Zunt JR, Kassebaum NJ, Blake N, Glennie L, Wright C, Nichols E, 
Abd-Allah F, Abdela J, Abdelalim A, Adamu AA, Adib MG, Ahmadi A, Ahmed MB, 
